{
  "stem": "13981.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that evidence was, of course, easy to pick up by the Yugoslav prosecution.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there were hundreds of them-- thousands of them-- available.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then the each individual armies had their-- excuse me-- their signal corps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they came-- excuse me-- came to camp or something, they took pictures with it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I had this one-- I remember one was done by a, a German amateur movie guy who [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] showed the, the way the prisoners were received at a concentration camp-- how they were-- the women were pulled naked by their hair and so forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have seen these little stills that I have of there-- of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's another one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was only a very short-- I don't think the whole thing lasted eight minute. and things like that, we, uh-- then also, I remember once I was sent to Berlin to pick up evidence that had been gathered there and bring it back to--",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was documents and some film.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know I had to go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How, how, the, the Russians themselves authen-- authenticated it, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it, it, it was official.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it's--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we got it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once it got into the court's hands, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't store it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we had some, we came up with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We notified the particular persons who needed it that we had some.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I was practically the last man on the line to get it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where it was kept before that, I, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess the either prosecution or maybe the defense got copies of it also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
